<doc id="65892" wikidata="Q1409226" url="?curid=65892" title="Weber (surname)">
<text>Weber (, or ; German: ) is a surname of German origin, derived from the noun meaning &quot;weaver&quot;. In some cases, following migration to English-speaking countries, it has been anglicised to the English surname &#x27;Webber&#x27; or &#x27;Weaver&#x27;.

Notable people with the surname include:

